===Etymology===
{{PIE root|en|bʰer}}
From {{inh|en|enm|fortune}}, borrowed from {{bor|en|fro|fortune}}, from {{der|en|la|fortuna||fate, luck}}. The plural form {{m|la|fortunae}} meant “possessions”, which also gave ''fortune'' the meaning of “riches”.

